<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title>Support - E-Voting System</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f9;
        }
        header {
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        main {
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            width: 80%;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h1, h2 {
            color: #333;
        }
        .faq-section {
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        .faq-section ul {
            list-style-type: none;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .faq-section li {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .faq-section a {
            color: #4CAF50;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .faq-section a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        .contact-form input,
        .contact-form textarea {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            margin: 10px 0;
            border-radius: 4px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
        }
        .contact-form button {
            padding: 12px 20px;
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        .contact-form button:hover {
            background-color: #45a049;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Support - E-Voting System</h1>
    </header>

    <main>
        <div class="container">
            <h2>How can we help you?</h2>
            <p>If you are having any issues or have questions about the E-Voting system, please check the FAQs below or fill out the contact form to get in touch with our support team.</p>

            <!-- FAQ Section -->
            <div class="faq-section">
                <h3>Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="#">How do I register for the e-voting system?</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#">What do I do if I forgot my voting credentials?</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#">Can I vote anonymously in the system?</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#">What should I do if I encounter a technical issue while voting?</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#">How can I verify my vote?</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#">What security measures are in place for my vote?</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <!-- Contact Form -->
            <div class="contact-form">
                <h3>Contact Us</h3>
                <p>If you couldn't find the answer you were looking for or need further assistance, please fill out the form below:</p>
                <form action="/supportreply" method="get">
                    <label for="name">Your Name:</label>
                    <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required>

                    <label for="email">Your Email:</label>
                    <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required>

                    <label for="subject">Subject:</label>
                    <input type="text" id="subject" name="subject" required>

                    <label for="message">Message:</label>
                    <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="5" required></textarea>

                    <button type="submit">Submit Support Request</button>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
</body>
</html>
